Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.cell

Class SpawnCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.cell.Cell
      • it.polimi.ingsw.model.cell.SpawnCell
  • public class SpawnCell
extends Cell
    SpawnCells are Cells that Players can choose as spawn points. Each SpawnCell also includes a display of Weapons available to be purchased by Players, so long as they have enough ammo to be able to afford the purchase cost of the Weapon.
